    <item>
      <title>伊朗威胁控制霍尔木兹海峡的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/business/iran-toll-strait-hormuz.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗正试图通过收取通行费来维护对海峡的控制。专家表示，这种情况不太可能发生，但这种威胁已经让航运业感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/23/business/iran-toll-strait-hormuz.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 04:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
