      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/22/us/methyl-methacrylate-garden-grove-chemical-leak.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国环保署警告说，短期接触该化合物可能会导致皮肤和眼睛刺激以及呼吸道问题。]]></description>
